node.text: Make packed lunches more fun and healthy with Yumbox

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by YUMBOX makes lunches FUN on August 14, 2021. May be an image of fruit and indoor.

node.text:
The happiest lunch prep combo. We love Yumbox Chop Chop food prep set as it simplifies every hectic morning. Just prep ahead and assemble Yumbox lunch or snack in minutes. 

For those waiting on restocking items - they will be available this Tuesday for sale 🤞

node.text:
Camp snacks for the win!

Repost @mydaughterslunchbox
・・・
Mini pretzels 🥨, carrots 🥕, blueberries 🫐, peaches 🍑 and cashews 😋

node.text:
When in doubt - go leakproof. 

Yumbox makes it easy to pack dips, condiments, pasta salads & more. Packed lunches should be fun to eat & easy to prepare.

node.text:
Fun packed lunches can be as easy as this. 

Yumbox Tapas lunch by @ourbalancedkitchen
・・・
A special sandwich today because we could all do with a little extra 💜 right now 

💜 Jam sandwich…my girls squealed with excitement when they saw this. Easily made with two heart shaped cookie cutters. Using @maggie_beer strawberry and verjuice jam and @queenfinefoods unicorn confetti 🦄 
💜 Carrot sticks
💜 Blackberries
💜 Apples - Quick hack coming soon on how to prevent apples browning in lunchboxes
💜 Leftover pasta with zucchini - a quick an easy recipe coming soon!
